<l>niṟaiyuṭaimai nīṅkāmai vēṇṭiṟ poṟaiyuṭaimai</l>
<l>pōṟṟi yoḻukap paṭum</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>If you desire that greatness should never leave, you preserve in your conduct the exercise of patience.</l>
